{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Good morning."},{"time":2000,"text":"I've come here to share with you an experiment"},{"time":6000,"text":"of how to get rid of one form of human suffering."},{"time":10000,"text":"It really is a story of Dr. Venkataswamy."},{"time":13000,"text":"His mission and his message is about the Aravind Eye Care System."},{"time":19000,"text":"I think first it's important for us to recognize what it is to be blind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":24000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":28000,"text":"Woman: Everywhere I went looking for work, they said no,"},{"time":32000,"text":"what use do we have for a blind woman?"},{"time":35000,"text":"I couldn't thread a needle or see the lice in my hair."},{"time":38000,"text":"If an ant fell into my rice, I couldn't see that either."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42000,"text":"Thulasiraj Ravilla: Becoming blind is a big part of it,"},{"time":44000,"text":"but I think it also deprives the person of their livelihood, their dignity,"},{"time":49000,"text":"their independence, and their status in the family."},{"time":52000,"text":"So she is just one amongst the millions who are blind."},{"time":56000,"text":"And the irony is that they don't need to be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":59000,"text":"A simple, well-proven surgery can restore sight to millions,"},{"time":63000,"text":"and something even simpler, a pair of glasses, can make millions more see."},{"time":68000,"text":"If we add to that the many of us here now"},{"time":71000,"text":"who are more productive because they have a pair of glasses,"},{"time":75000,"text":"then almost one in five Indians will require eye care,"},{"time":78000,"text":"a staggering 200 million people."},{"time":81000,"text":"Today, we're reaching not even 10 percent of them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85000,"text":"So this is the context in which Aravind came into existence"},{"time":88000,"text":"about 30 years back"},{"time":91000,"text":"as a post-retirement project of Dr. V."},{"time":94000,"text":"He started this with no money."},{"time":96000,"text":"He had to mortgage all his life savings"},{"time":99000,"text":"to make a bank loan."},{"time":101000,"text":"And over time, we have grown into a network of five hospitals,"},{"time":105000,"text":"predominately in the state of Tamil Nadu and Puducherry,"},{"time":109000,"text":"and then we added several, what we call Vision Centers"},{"time":113000,"text":"as a hub-and-spoke model."},{"time":115000,"text":"And then more recently we started managing hospitals"},{"time":118000,"text":"in other parts of the country"},{"time":120000,"text":"and also setting up hospitals in other parts of the world as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":124000,"text":"The last three decades,"},{"time":126000,"text":"we have done about three-and-a-half million surgeries,"},{"time":130000,"text":"a vast majority of them for the poor people."},{"time":134000,"text":"Now, each year we perform about 300,000 surgeries."},{"time":139000,"text":"A typical day at Aravind, we would do about a thousand surgeries,"},{"time":143000,"text":"maybe see about 6,000 patients,"},{"time":147000,"text":"send out teams into the villages to examine, bring back patients,"},{"time":152000,"text":"lots of telemedicine consultations,"},{"time":155000,"text":"and, on top of that, do a lot of training,"},{"time":158000,"text":"both for doctors and technicians who will become the future staff of Aravind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":165000,"text":"And then doing this day-in and day-out, and doing it well,"},{"time":169000,"text":"requires a lot of inspiration and a lot of hard work."},{"time":173000,"text":"And I think this was possible thanks to the building blocks"},{"time":176000,"text":"put in place by Dr. V.,"},{"time":179000,"text":"a value system, an efficient delivery process,"},{"time":183000,"text":"and fostering the culture of innovation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":194000,"text":"Dr. V: I used to sit with the ordinary village man because I am from a village,"},{"time":198000,"text":"and suddenly you turn around and seem to be in contact with his inner being,"},{"time":202000,"text":"you seem to be one with him."},{"time":205000,"text":"Here is a soul which has got all the simplicity of confidence."},{"time":210000,"text":"Doctor, whatever you say, I accept it."},{"time":213000,"text":"An implicit faith in you"},{"time":215000,"text":"and then you respond to it."},{"time":217000,"text":"Here is an old lady who has got so much faith in me, I must do my best for her."},{"time":222000,"text":"When we grow in spiritual consciousness,"},{"time":225000,"text":"we identify ourselves with all that is in the world,"},{"time":228000,"text":"so there is no exploitation."},{"time":231000,"text":"It is ourselves we are helping."},{"time":234000,"text":"It is ourselves we are healing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":242000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":248000,"text":"This helped us build a very ethical and very highly patient-centric organization"},{"time":254000,"text":"and systems that support it."},{"time":256000,"text":"But on a practical level, you also have to deliver services efficiently,"},{"time":262000,"text":"and, odd as it may seem, the inspiration came from McDonald's."}]},{"cues":[{"time":266000,"text":"Dr. V: See, McDonald's' concept is simple."},{"time":270000,"text":"They feel they can train people all over the world,"},{"time":278000,"text":"irrespective of different religions, cultures, all those things,"},{"time":281000,"text":"to produce a product in the same way"},{"time":285000,"text":"and deliver it in the same manner"},{"time":288000,"text":"in hundreds of places."}]},{"cues":[{"time":290000,"text":"Larry Brilliant: He kept talking about McDonalds and hamburgers,"},{"time":292000,"text":"and none of it made any sense to us."},{"time":298000,"text":"He wanted to create a franchise,"},{"time":301000,"text":"a mechanism of delivery of eye care"},{"time":304000,"text":"with the efficiency of McDonald's."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307000,"text":"Dr. V: Supposing I'm able to produce eye care,"},{"time":309000,"text":"techniques, methods, all in the same way,"},{"time":313000,"text":"and make it available in every corner of the world."},{"time":316000,"text":"The problem of blindness is gone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":319000,"text":"TR: If you think about it, I think the eyeball is the same,"},{"time":322000,"text":"as American or African,"},{"time":324000,"text":"the problem is the same, the treatment is the same."},{"time":327000,"text":"And yet, why should there be so much variation in quality and in service,"},{"time":331000,"text":"and that was the fundamental principle that we followed"},{"time":334000,"text":"when we designed the delivery systems."},{"time":337000,"text":"And, of course, the challenge was that it's a huge problem,"},{"time":340000,"text":"we are talking of millions of people,"},{"time":343000,"text":"very little resource to deal with it,"},{"time":346000,"text":"and then lots of logistics and affordability issues."}]},{"cues":[{"time":350000,"text":"And then so, one had to constantly innovate."},{"time":353000,"text":"And one of the early innovations, which still continues,"},{"time":356000,"text":"is to create ownership in the community to the problem,"},{"time":360000,"text":"and then engage with them as a partner,"},{"time":363000,"text":"and here is one such event."},{"time":365000,"text":"Here a community camp just organized"},{"time":368000,"text":"by the community themselves,"},{"time":371000,"text":"where they find a place, organize volunteers,"},{"time":374000,"text":"and then we'll do our part. You know, check their vision,"},{"time":379000,"text":"and then you have doctors who you find out what the problem is"},{"time":382000,"text":"and then determine what further testing should be done,"},{"time":385000,"text":"and then those tests are done by technicians"},{"time":390000,"text":"who check for glasses,"},{"time":394000,"text":"or check for glaucoma."}]},{"cues":[{"time":398000,"text":"And then, with all these results, the doctor makes a final diagnosis,"},{"time":402000,"text":"and then prescribes a line of treatment,"},{"time":405000,"text":"and if they need a pair of glasses, they are available right there at the camp site,"},{"time":409000,"text":"usually under a tree."},{"time":411000,"text":"But they get glasses in the frames of their choice,"},{"time":414000,"text":"and that's very important because I think glasses,"},{"time":417000,"text":"in addition to helping people see,"},{"time":419000,"text":"is also a fashion statement, and they're willing to pay for it."},{"time":427000,"text":"So they get it in about 20 minutes"},{"time":430000,"text":"and those who require surgery, are counseled,"},{"time":433000,"text":"and then there are buses waiting,"},{"time":436000,"text":"which will transport them to the base hospital."}]},{"cues":[{"time":439000,"text":"And if it was not for this kind of logistics and support,"},{"time":444000,"text":"many people like this would probably never get services,"},{"time":447000,"text":"and certainly not when they most need it."},{"time":451000,"text":"They receive surgery the following day,"},{"time":455000,"text":"and then they will stay for a day or two,"},{"time":458000,"text":"and then they are put back on the buses"},{"time":460000,"text":"to be taken back to where they came from,"},{"time":463000,"text":"and where their families will be waiting to take them back home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":474000,"text":"And this happens several thousand times each year."},{"time":479000,"text":"It may sound impressive that we're seeing lots of patients,"},{"time":482000,"text":"very efficient process,"},{"time":484000,"text":"but we looked at, are we solving the problem?"},{"time":488000,"text":"We did a study, a scientifically designed process,"},{"time":490000,"text":"and then, to our dismay,"},{"time":492000,"text":"we found this was only reaching seven percent of those in need,"},{"time":497000,"text":"and we're not adequately addressing more, bigger problems."}]},{"cues":[{"time":501000,"text":"So we had to do something different,"},{"time":503000,"text":"so we set up what we call primary eye care centers, vision centers."},{"time":508000,"text":"These are truly paperless offices"},{"time":510000,"text":"with completely electronic medical records and so on."},{"time":514000,"text":"They receive comprehensive eye exams."},{"time":517000,"text":"We kind of changed the simple digital camera into a retinal camera,"},{"time":521000,"text":"and then every patient gets their teleconsultation with a doctor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":527000,"text":"The effect of this has been that, within the first year,"},{"time":531000,"text":"we really had a 40 percent penetration in the market that it served,"},{"time":536000,"text":"which is over 50,000 people."},{"time":538000,"text":"And the second year went up to 75 percent."},{"time":540000,"text":"So I think we have a process by which"},{"time":542000,"text":"we can really penetrate into the market"},{"time":544000,"text":"and reach everyone who needs it,"},{"time":547000,"text":"and in this process of using technology, make sure"},{"time":550000,"text":"that most don't need to come to the base hospital."}]},{"cues":[{"time":553000,"text":"And how much will they pay for this?"},{"time":555000,"text":"We fixed the pricing, taking into account"},{"time":558000,"text":"what they would save in bus fare in coming to a city,"},{"time":562000,"text":"so they pay about 20 rupees, and that's good for three consultations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":566000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":569000,"text":"The other challenge was, how do you give high-tech"},{"time":572000,"text":"or more advanced treatment and care?"},{"time":575000,"text":"We designed a van with a VSAT,"},{"time":578000,"text":"which sends out images of patients to the base hospital"},{"time":582000,"text":"where it is diagnosed,"},{"time":585000,"text":"and then as the patient is waiting, the report goes back to the patient,"},{"time":589000,"text":"it gets printed out, the patient gets it,"},{"time":592000,"text":"and then gets a consultation about what they should be doing --"},{"time":595000,"text":"I mean, go see a doctor or come back after six months,"},{"time":598000,"text":"and then this happens as a way of"},{"time":600000,"text":"bridging the technology competence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":605000,"text":"So the impact of all this has been essentially one of growing the market,"},{"time":609000,"text":"because it focused on the non-customer,"},{"time":612000,"text":"and then by reaching the unreached,"},{"time":615000,"text":"we're able to significantly grow the market."}]},{"cues":[{"time":617000,"text":"The other aspect is how do you deal with this efficiently"},{"time":621000,"text":"when you have very few ophthalmologists?"},{"time":624000,"text":"So what is in this video is a surgeon operating,"},{"time":627000,"text":"and then you see on the other side,"},{"time":629000,"text":"another patient is getting ready."},{"time":631000,"text":"So, as they finish the surgery,"},{"time":634000,"text":"they just swing the microscope over,"},{"time":637000,"text":"the tables are placed so that their distance is just right,"},{"time":641000,"text":"and then we need to do this, because, by doing this kind of process,"},{"time":644000,"text":"we're able to more than quadruple the productivity of the surgeon."}]},{"cues":[{"time":649000,"text":"And then to support the surgeon,"},{"time":651000,"text":"we require a certain workforce."},{"time":654000,"text":"And then we focused on village girls that we recruited,"},{"time":658000,"text":"and then they really are the backbone of the organization."},{"time":661000,"text":"They do almost all of the skill-based routine tasks."},{"time":665000,"text":"They do one thing at a time. They do it extremely well."},{"time":668000,"text":"With the result we have very high productivity,"},{"time":671000,"text":"very high quality at very, very low cost."},{"time":676000,"text":"So, putting all this together, what really happened was"},{"time":679000,"text":"the productivity of our staff was"},{"time":682000,"text":"significantly higher than anyone else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":685000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":691000,"text":"This is a very busy table,"},{"time":693000,"text":"but what this really is conveying is that,"},{"time":695000,"text":"when it comes to quality, we have put in"},{"time":697000,"text":"very good quality-assurance systems."},{"time":700000,"text":"As a result, our complications are significantly lower"},{"time":703000,"text":"than what has been reported in the United Kingdom,"},{"time":706000,"text":"and you don't see those kind of numbers very often."}]},{"cues":[{"time":709000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":711000,"text":"So the final part of the puzzle is,"},{"time":713000,"text":"how do you make all this work financially,"},{"time":716000,"text":"especially when the people can't pay for it?"},{"time":719000,"text":"So what we did was, we gave away a lot of it for free,"},{"time":723000,"text":"and then those who pay, I mean, they paid local market rates,"},{"time":726000,"text":"nothing more, and often much less."},{"time":728000,"text":"And we were helped by the market inefficiency."},{"time":731000,"text":"I think that has been a big savior, even now."},{"time":734000,"text":"And, of course, one needs the mindset to be wanting to give away"},{"time":738000,"text":"what you have as a surplus."}]},{"cues":[{"time":741000,"text":"The result has been, over the years,"},{"time":743000,"text":"the expenditure has increased with volumes."},{"time":745000,"text":"The revenues increase at a higher level,"},{"time":747000,"text":"giving us a healthy margin"},{"time":749000,"text":"while you're treating a large number of people for free."},{"time":753000,"text":"I think in absolute terms,"},{"time":755000,"text":"last year we earned about 20-odd million dollars,"},{"time":758000,"text":"spent about 13 million, with over a 40 percent EBITA."}]},{"cues":[{"time":763000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":771000,"text":"But this really requires going beyond what we do,"},{"time":774000,"text":"or what we have done,"},{"time":777000,"text":"if you really want to achieve solving this problem of blindness."},{"time":780000,"text":"And what we did was a couple of very counter-intuitive things."},{"time":784000,"text":"We created competition for ourselves,"},{"time":787000,"text":"and then we made eye care affordable"},{"time":790000,"text":"by making low-cost consumables."},{"time":793000,"text":"We proactively and systematically"},{"time":796000,"text":"promoted these practices to many hospitals in India,"},{"time":800000,"text":"many in our own backyards and then in other parts of the world as well."},{"time":803000,"text":"The impact of this has been that these hospitals,"},{"time":807000,"text":"in the second year after our consultation,"},{"time":810000,"text":"are double their output"},{"time":812000,"text":"and then achieve financial recovery as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":818000,"text":"The other part was how do you address"},{"time":821000,"text":"this increase in cost of technology?"},{"time":825000,"text":"There was a time when we failed to negotiate"},{"time":828000,"text":"the [intra-ocular lens] prices to be at affordable levels,"},{"time":830000,"text":"so we set up a manufacturing unit."},{"time":834000,"text":"And then, over time, we were able to bring down the cost significantly"},{"time":838000,"text":"to about two percent of what it used to be when we started out."},{"time":843000,"text":"Today, we believe we have about seven percent of the global market,"},{"time":847000,"text":"and they're used in about 120-odd countries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":851000,"text":"To conclude, I mean, what we do, does it have a broader relevance,"},{"time":856000,"text":"or is it just India or developing countries?"},{"time":861000,"text":"So to address this, we studied UK versus Aravind."},{"time":868000,"text":"What it shows is that we do roughly about 60 percent"},{"time":871000,"text":"of the volume of what the UK does,"},{"time":874000,"text":"near a half-million surgeries as a whole country."},{"time":877000,"text":"And we do about 300,000."},{"time":880000,"text":"And then we train about 50 ophthalmologists"},{"time":883000,"text":"against the 70 trained by them,"},{"time":886000,"text":"comparable quality, both in training and in patient care."},{"time":889000,"text":"So we're really comparing apples to apples."},{"time":892000,"text":"We looked at cost."},{"time":894000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":896000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":902000,"text":"So, I think it is simple to say"},{"time":904000,"text":"just because the U.K. isn't India the difference is happening."},{"time":908000,"text":"I think there is more to it."},{"time":910000,"text":"I mean, I think one has to look at other aspects as well."},{"time":912000,"text":"Maybe there is --"},{"time":914000,"text":"the solution to the cost could be in productivity,"},{"time":918000,"text":"maybe in efficiency, in the clinical process,"},{"time":921000,"text":"or in how much they pay for the lenses or consumables,"},{"time":924000,"text":"or regulations, their defensive practice."},{"time":927000,"text":"So, I think decoding this can probably bring"},{"time":930000,"text":"answers to most developed countries"},{"time":935000,"text":"including the U.S., and maybe"},{"time":937000,"text":"Obama's ratings can go up again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":940000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":944000,"text":"Another insight, which, again, I want to leave with you,"},{"time":948000,"text":"in conditions where the problem is very large,"},{"time":951000,"text":"which cuts across all economic strata,"},{"time":953000,"text":"where we have a good solution,"},{"time":956000,"text":"I think the process I described,"},{"time":958000,"text":"you know, productivity, quality, patient-centered care,"},{"time":962000,"text":"can give an answer,"},{"time":965000,"text":"and there are many which fit this paradigm."},{"time":967000,"text":"You take dentistry, hearing aid, maternity and so on."},{"time":970000,"text":"There are many where this paradigm can now play,"},{"time":973000,"text":"but I think probably one of the most challenging things"},{"time":975000,"text":"is on the softer side."}]},{"cues":[{"time":977000,"text":"Now, how do you create compassion?"},{"time":979000,"text":"Now, how do you make people own the problem,"},{"time":981000,"text":"want to do something about it?"},{"time":983000,"text":"There are a bit harder issues."},{"time":985000,"text":"And I'm sure people in this crowd can probably find the solutions to these."}]},{"cues":[{"time":989000,"text":"So I want to end my talk leaving this thought and challenge to you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":992000,"text":"Dr. V: When you grow in spiritual consciousness,"},{"time":995000,"text":"we identify with all that is in the world"},{"time":998000,"text":"so there is no exploitation."},{"time":1001000,"text":"It is ourselves we are helping."},{"time":1003000,"text":"It is ourselves we are healing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1006000,"text":"TR: Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1008000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}